{"tid":803472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又送大禮］本港沙灘廢棄膠樽四成屬內地品牌","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:00:01.000Z","uid":4610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a26567e7036e2e498a477f7644aeac72f117e7f","tid":803472,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"有環保團體的調查發現，在本港沙灘檢獲的廢棄膠樽近<span style=\"color: red;\">四成為簡體字品牌</span>。 綠惜地球上個月在香港及台灣合共進行十六場淨灘行動，在沙灘收集逾五千二百個廢棄膠樽，<span style=\"color: red;\">簡體字品牌的膠樽佔逾六成</span>，其中在香港收集的近一千八百個膠樽，近四成為簡體字品牌。<br />\n<br />\n對於<span style=\"color: red;\">環保署早前聲稱來自內地的海上垃圾只佔整體百分之五</span>，綠惜地球認為值得商榷，要求粵港兩地加強合作，防止廢塑膠污染海洋生態，飲品生產商亦應負責任，制訂積極減塑目標及時間表，做好源頭減廢及回收。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318829&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318829%26refer%3Dshare&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1k%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b749388c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D318829%26refer%3Dshare&h=c1d2ca76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=318829&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"8cce0dd0df15f656fe47a66ea0080dda235de86b","tid":803472,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"團體指這些膠樽都是於較偏遠的沙灘拾獲，包括鶴咀垃圾灣及東龍島等，估計膠樽由內地漂流至香港"},{"pid":"8a0b4df65d98ccf0b1a9ede87f8627bd82a6b26e","tid":803472,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48b2fb40c3ba9a6fb65c0a5b38e50650564a556","tid":803472,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"明眼人一看便知是移花接木"},{"pid":"3e9db0074e736fd73e1df0517d2bcc3d64447bcd","tid":803472,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"環保署：內地品牌唔代表由內地人棄置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}